Version -next
  - Using BusyBox 1.20.2 which has more applets.
  - Fix in create-iso.sh in some sed expressions.
  - Add extra debugging shell in init.
  - libSaLT is reloaded after exiting a debug shell if it has been modified.
  - Chrooting does not need a chroot (nor pivot_root) binary on the target system anymore.
  - Time zone menus and time zone is set in the target distro.
Version 0.2.0 (2012-06-09)
  - create-iso.sh: use isolinux+grub2 systematically, and use the isohybrid format.
Version 0.1.2 (2012-04-13)
  - rc.salt: remove a warning shown if firefox is not available.
Version 0.1.1 (2012-03-13)
